bisq.core.dao.vote.proposal

Class ProposalPayload

  • java.lang.Object
    • bisq.core.dao.vote.proposal.ProposalPayload
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    bisq.common.Payload, bisq.common.Proto, bisq.common.proto.network.NetworkPayload, bisq.common.proto.persistable.PersistablePayload, bisq.network.p2p.storage.payload.CapabilityRequiringPayload, bisq.network.p2p.storage.payload.LazyProcessedPayload, bisq.network.p2p.storage.payload.ProtectedStoragePayload
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ChangeParamProposalPayload, CompensationRequestPayload, GenericProposalPayload, RemoveAssetProposalPayload

    public abstract class ProposalPayload
extends java.lang.Object
implements bisq.network.p2p.storage.payload.LazyProcessedPayload, bisq.network.p2p.storage.payload.ProtectedStoragePayload, bisq.common.proto.persistable.PersistablePayload, bisq.network.p2p.storage.payload.CapabilityRequiringPayload
    Payload is sent over wire as well as it gets persisted.

    We persist all ProposalPayload data in PersistableNetworkPayloadMap. Data size on disk for one item is: about 743 bytes (443 bytes is for ownerPubKeyEncoded) As there are not 1000s of proposals we consider that acceptable.
